93,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"de9a0d31db00d2664b25130803bd056038ffe4ae","tid":989241,"uid":202876,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T16:39:08.000Z","msg":"明明中國男多女少<br />\n點解仲可以定期送處女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T16:40:24.000Z","msg":"巴打啱啱訓咗幾多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個世界有處女膜修補手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T19:32:30.000Z","msg":"唔駛。<br />\n支那女人拜金拜到不得了。<br />\n有係大陸住的表哥，屋企開廠，中學開始食女，真係數之不盡。<br />\n大陸有錢人咩都有得玩。有好多原因令佢地咁：<br />\n<br />\n1. 支那女人拜金，成日睇外國電影之類，初中高中已經好想要lv之類的名牌<br />\n2. 支那的一孩制度，寵咗好多俾屋企人寵慣的女人<br />\n3. 重點：大陸的初中高中係寄宿學校。點玩都無人知。<br />\n4. 戶籍制度，大陸人普遍會去外省打工廠工（即廣東一帶）父母都會出去工作，只會係新年/五一回鄉。剩低兩老照顧仔女，管到條毛。<br />\n<br />\n修補處女膜真係你地先會諗。<br />\n<br />\nPs. 條撚樣表哥梗係唔會益我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對另一個靚女表妹，每年新年都派4000人仔利是。<br />\n我就渣都無。"},{"pid":"79ed20c12c3bc07ece90cc8c4dcf893e663dbd37","tid":989241,"uid":68944,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T19:38:11.000Z","msg":"冇錢冇權冇樣，成世都冇機會擁有幸福賓周<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de4c34a69dd9ba621143e3c81c4786243c4e4d9","tid":989241,"uid":16404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T19:46:22.000Z","msg":"想做中国法官 加入共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864fa38c4d2b63d635918f367e724b4e76ee7cab","tid":989241,"